Package: GOV
Type: Package
Title: Graph on Vector Regression with Latent Scale Gaussian Process
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sagnik", "Bhadury", email = "bhadury@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for regressing a scalar response on a network-valued
    predictor. An EM algorithm (EM_toU()) estimates low-rank latent node
    positions from an observed adjacency matrix via a latent space network
    model. A latent-space Gaussian process regression with spike-and-slab
    variable selection over nodes (lsGPR_VS()) then regresses a response on
    a distance kernel built from those (and optionally other) latent
    positions, selecting which nodes' positions actually drive the kernel.
